      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: It's gone. I can feel it. The weight on this forest... it's lifting.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: You did what I could not.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: I don't sense any divinity within you, but I can tell that it was you
        who slayed it.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: What an odd creature...
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: The forest will heal now. The creatures will calm. It will take time,
        but the worst is over.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: As for me... I can finally rest.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: 'Thank you, human. The forest will remain forever in your debt... '
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 2
